name: Acis-component-examples
body:
Some simple examples of using ACIS WebServices from Components

  • Min and Max average temps for Ithaca with mouse over data point.
  • A fixed list of stations and elements generating a table of values.
  • Several components working together to select a geo-region and generate a D3 precip plot
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
